Wrap the release loop in a try/catch and log failures, or use `Promise.allSettled` to ensure all releases are attempted regardless of individual failures:

```ts
// Release already-reserved items — best-effort
for (const r of reserved) {
  try {
    await supabase.rpc('release_stock', {
      p_product_id: r.productId,
      p_quantity: r.quantity,
    });
  } catch (releaseErr) {
    console.error('Failed to release stock for', r.productId, releaseErr);
  }
}
throw new Error('stock_error');
```

